@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cffcyl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.11 + v0 + 0.22)) + (tmp - (v1 + 0.11 * v1 + 0.01)))
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v1 + 0.24) * (v0 + 0.23 - tmp + 0.10)) - wp.abs(wp.abs(v2 + 0.42)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.43)) + (0.54 - (tmp + 0.06 * v0 + 0.18)))
    v2 = v0
    v1 = wp.abs(v0)
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.58) / (v1 + 0.64 - v1 + 0.15)) * v2)
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
